<!-- About Page Content -->
<div class="section" id="about">
  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <p>
    Smart Food Waste Management is committed to reducing food waste and
    addressing hunger through our innovative platform. Our mission is to connect
    donors, users, and volunteers in a seamless ecosystem that ensures surplus
    food is effectively redistributed to those in need.
  </p>
  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="about-item">
      <i class="fas fa-truck"></i>
      <h3>Food Collection</h3>
      <p>
        We collect surplus food from various sources, including restaurants,
        cafes, and grocery stores. Our efficient logistics ensure that food is
        collected promptly and safely.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-item">
      <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
      <h3>Distribution to Needy</h3>
      <p>
        The collected food is distributed to charitable organizations, shelters,
        and community centers that serve individuals and families in need. Our
        goal is to reduce food insecurity and promote community well-being.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-item">
      <i class="fas fa-recycle"></i>
      <h3>Waste Reduction</h3>
      <p>
        By redistributing surplus food, we contribute to reducing waste and
        minimizing the environmental impact of food disposal. Our efforts
        support a more sustainable and responsible approach to food management.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

